snippet.title: Unheard Screams - Concept Trailer
snippet.description: Unheard Screams is a text based game with battles set in the Congo during the regime of King Leopold II of Belgium. As Miala, the liberating hero, the player will fight the forces of the white men oppressors and regained dominion of territories for the Congolese people.
